LOL usually anyone who says &quot;i&#39;m the best&quot; or &quot;i&#39;m the expert&quot; or &quot;i&#39;m
superior&quot; is the last person I pay attention to because thats ego speaking.
Everyone has the capability to form good communication with other spirits
whether in life or passed on, it&#39;s the intent that matters. So go in with
good intent and you wont be disappointed. Be respectful and honest and you
tend to get it in return, be nasty and negative and ditto on the response ya
get. 



Nobody is an expert here, whether ya been at this 2 years or 100, everyone
is learning as they go and hopefully sharing what we learn along the way.
Like I said life is about learning. 



Misty

