Well, if this leads to fighting, I&#39;m sure Spirit will stop talking to us
altogether, I tried to call Bill&#39;s machine, but I couldn&#39;t hear much of
anything, maybe sound was too low, or maybe someone was hearing what I
should have been hearing, I&#39;m sure they heard me, but someone on the other
end was reaping the rewards of my one sided conversation, I&#39;m sure.  Left me
very unhappy, (p...is..ed o..f). , I sure wish people could make this work
for all of us though, and give credit where credit is due, Edison told me,
he was working with a certain couple of people, poor guy, he&#39;s running all
over the place, when people keep asking for his help, he has to stop what
he&#39;s doing to inspire one person, then has to run over to see what all the
hollering is all about with someone else.  Don&#39;t forget, none of this would
be possible were it not given to us by the Man upstairs, and no one gives
Him any credit, it&#39;s not &quot;religion.&quot;  It&#39;s called life.

sf



